      Modifier and Type Class and Description
      class  MetricFilterGroup
      Implementation of MetricFilter interface that allows grouping of multiple filters.
      class  MetricNameFilter
      Implementation of MetricFilter that uses an exact match of a pre-defined string against a Metric.name().
      class  MetricRegexFilter
      Implementation of MetricFilter that uses a regular expression to match against a Metric.name().
